+## Overview
+
+Total revenue was $7,154.44 across 30 orders. The median order value was $204.95.
+
+## Top Products
+
+Gadget ranked first with $2,392.00 in revenue, followed by Widget at $2,118.94, Doohickey at $1,513.00, and Sprocket at $1,130.50.
+
+## Regional Performance
+
+North led with $2,176.35, followed by East at $1,830.79, South at $1,732.48, and West at $1,414.82.
+
+## Recommendations
+
+- Prioritize Gadget availability; it generated the highest product revenue at $2,392.00.
+- Study North's sales mix; its $2,176.35 revenue exceeded every other region.
+- Target West for growth initiatives; its $1,414.82 revenue was the lowest regional result.
